text: Friendly welcoming service. Small and cosy place. Has Heineken and carlsberg, great beer choices. Doesn't open daily, be sure to call and check opening hours prior to visit.

A cosy and clean bar to sing and have some chill beers after a whole day work.
the system is good and the drinks are priced reasonably.
Convenient location in the heart of bugis.
Thumbs up to the operator of this cosy pub.
